## 📌 Prompt Text (v1.2 — current)

Analyse the following weekly sales data for a retail store.

Identify:

* Top 3 best-selling products (by sales volume)
* Top 3 declining products (largest decrease vs previous period)
* Any notable patterns (e.g. seasonal trends, demand shifts)
* 2 key insights for inventory planning
* 2 potential risks if trends continue

Use ONLY the data provided. Do not assume or generate missing data.

Sales data:
[SALES_DATA]

Respond in bullet points only.
Limit to 200 words.
Do not include any explanation outside the requested output.

