## ⚠️ Risks and Limitations

| Risk                            | Level  | Mitigation                                  |
| ------------------------------- | ------ | ------------------------------------------- |
| Incorrect trend interpretation  | Medium | Human validation before decisions           |
| Poor input data quality         | High   | Validate sales data before prompt           |
| Hallucination (invented trends) | Medium | “Use only provided data” constraint         |
| Oversimplified insights         | Medium | Combine with deeper analysis in later steps |

**Overall risk rating: MEDIUM** — suitable for assisted decision-making with human review.

